It is the 59th combination in the Sexagenary cycle; the preceding one is {{ill|Xinyou|ja|辛酉}} and the following one is {{ill|Guihai|ja|癸亥}}. In the system of {{ill|Yin-Yang and the Five Elements|ja|陰陽五行思想|lt=Yin-Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=陰陽五行}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|lt=Ten Heavenly Stems|ja|十干}}’ {{ill|Ren|ja|壬|1=Mizunoe (壬)}} represents yang {{ill|Water|ja|水}}, while the {{ill|Twelve Earthly Branches|ja|十二支}}’ {{ill|Inu|ja|戌|1=Dog (zodiac)|lt=Dog (戌)}} represents yang {{ill|Earth|ja|土}}, and they are in the relationship of {{ill|Mutual Restraint|ja|五行思想#相剋（そうこく）|lt=Mutual Restraint|lt_ja=相剋}} (Earth overcomes Water).

== Years of Jinshitsu ==
A year in the {{ill|Common Era|ja|西暦}} that leaves a remainder of 2 when divided by 60 is a {{ill|Year|ja|年}} of Jinshitsu.
