'''Yang Water Dog also known as  Jinshitsu''' (壬戌) (みずのえいぬ、じんすいのいぬ、じんじゅつ) is one of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|干支|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.

It is the 59th combination in the Sexagenary cycle; the preceding one is {{ill|Xinyou|ja|辛酉|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and the following one is {{ill|Guihai|ja|癸亥|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. In the system of {{ill|Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|ja|陰陽五行思想|lt=Yin-Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=陰陽五行|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|lt=Ten Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}’ {{ill|Ren|ja|壬|1=Mizunoe (壬)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yang {{ill|Water|ja|水|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, while the {{ill|Twelve Earthly Branches|ja|十二支|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}’ {{ill|Inu|ja|戌|1=Dog (zodiac)|lt=Dog (戌)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yang {{ill|Earth|ja|土|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, and they are in the relationship of {{ill|Mutual Restraint|ja|五行思想#相剋（そうこく）|lt=Mutual Restraint|lt_ja=相剋|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Earth overcomes Water).

