== Months of Jinshitsu ==
In a Common Era year, if the final digit is 3 or 8 (that is, when the Ten Heavenly Stems are {{ill|Gui|ja|癸|1=Mizunoto (癸)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} or {{ill|Bo|ja|戊|1=Tsuchinoe (戊)|qq=draft|qq=draft}}), then {{ill|September|ja|9月|qq=draft|qq=draft}} becomes the {{ill|Month|ja|月 (暦)|lt=Month|qq=draft|qq=draft}} of Jinshitsu. However, the term “month” here may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft}} or to a seasonal month (from {{ill|Hanro|ja|寒露|qq=draft|qq=draft}} until the day before {{ill|Rittō|ja|立冬|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) as applicable.

== Days of Jinshitsu ==
=== Day Selection ===
A day of Jinshitsu is one of the intercalary days from {{ill|Hassen|ja|八専|qq=draft|qq=draft}}.
