ly Branches|13=User:Immanuelle/Earthly Branches|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Twelve Earthly Branches|13=User:Immanuelle/Earthly Branches|qq=}}’ {{ill|Inu|ja|戌|1=Dog (Zodiac)|lt=Dog (戌)|2=ja|3=戌|1=Dog (zodiac)|lt=Dog (戌)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Inu|13=User:Immanuelle/Dog (zodiac)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Inu|13=User:Immanuelle/Dog (Zodiac)|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Earth|ja|Earth (土)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (土)|2=ru|3=Земля (у-син)|4=mn|5=Шороо (махбод)|6=uk|7=Земля (У-сін)|8=als|9=Ärde in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=Thổ (Ngũ hành)|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (土)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earth|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earth|13=User:Immanuelle/Earth (wuxing)|qq=}}, and they are in the relationship of {{ill|Mutual Restraint|ja|五行思想#相剋（そうこく）|lt=Mutual Restraint|lt_ja=相剋|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mutual Restraint|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mutual Restraint|qq=}} (Earth overcomes Water).

