==Pronunciation== ==Years of Yang Water Dog== A year in the [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] that leaves a remainder of 2 when divided by 60 is a [[:en:Year|Year]] of Jinshitsu. {| class="wikitable" |+ '''Years of Jinshitsu''' |- ! [[:en:1st millennium|1st Millennium]] !! [[:en:2nd millennium|2nd Millennium]] !! [[:en:3rd millennium|3rd Millennium]] |- | * {{ill|2 AD|ja|2年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2 AD|qq=}} * [[:en:AD 62|62 AD]] * [[:en:AD 122|122 AD]] * [[:en:182|182 AD]] * [[:en:242|242 AD]] * [[:en:302|302 AD]] * [[:en:362|362 AD]] * [[:en:422|422 AD]] * [[:en:482|482 AD]] * [[:en:542|542 AD]] * [[:en:602|602 AD]] * [[:en:662|662 AD]] * [[:en:722|722 AD]] * [[:en:782|782 AD]] * [[:en:842|842 AD]] * [[:en:902|902 AD]] * [[:en:962|962 AD]] | * [[:en:1022|1022 AD]] * [[:en:1082|1082 AD]] * [[:en:1142|1142 AD]] * [[:en:1202|1202 AD]] * [[:en:1262|1262 AD]] * [[:en:1322|1322 AD]] * [[:en:1382|1382 AD]] * [[:en:1442|1442 AD]] * [[:en:1502|1502 AD]] * [[:en:1562|1562 AD]] * [[:en:1622|1622 AD]] * [[:en:1682|1682 AD]] * [[:en:1742|1742 AD]] * [[:en:1802|1802 AD]] * [[:en:1862|1862 AD]] * [[:en:1922|1922 AD]] * [[:en:1982|1982 AD]] | * {{ill|2042 AD|ja|2042年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2042|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2042 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2102 AD|ja|2102年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2102|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2102 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2162 AD|ja|2162年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2162|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2162 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2222 AD|ja|2222年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2222|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2222 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2282 AD|ja|2282年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2282|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2282 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2342 AD|ja|2342年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2342|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2342 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2402 AD|ja|2402年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2402|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2402 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2462 AD|ja|2462年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2462|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2462 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2522 AD|ja|2522年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2522|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2522 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2582 AD|ja|2582年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2582|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2582 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2642 AD|ja|2642年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2642|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2642 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2702 AD|ja|2702年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2702|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2702 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2762 AD|ja|2762年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2762|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2762 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2822 AD|ja|2822年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2822|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2822 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2882 AD|ja|2882年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2882|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2882 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2942 AD|ja|2942年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2942|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2942 AD|qq=}} |} ==Months of Yang Water Dog== == Months of Jinshitsu == In a Common Era year, if the final digit is 3 or 8 (that is, when the Ten Heavenly Stems are {{ill|Gui|ja|癸|1=Mizunoto (癸)|lt=Mizunoto (癸)|2=ja|3=癸|4=zh|5=癸|1=Mizunoto (癸)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gui|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoto (癸)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gui|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoto (癸)|qq=}} or {{ill|Bo|ja|戊|1=Tsuchinoe (戊)|lt=Tsuchinoe (戊)|2=ja|3=戊|4=zh|5=戊|1=Tsuchinoe (戊)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bo|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoe (戊)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bo|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoe (戊)|qq=}}), then [[:en:September|September]] becomes the [[:en:Month|Month]] of Jinshitsu. However, the term “month” here may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to a seasonal month (from [[:en:Hanlu|Hanro]] until the day before [[:en:Lidong|Rittō]]) as applicable. ==Days of Yang Water Dog== == Days of Jinshitsu == === Day Selection === A day of Jinshitsu is one of the intercalary days from {{ill|Hassen|ja|八専|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hassen|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hassen|qq=}}. == See Also == * {{prefix|qq=}} * {{intitle|qq=}}
